{
  "stem": "21731.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She had-- she worked in the-- in the office, the gasworks, and-- but she worked for Polish children, and for-- there was a nursery where the children were looked after when their parents were either taken away, or worked, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they needed cotton wool, and they needed some ordinary bandages, or vitamins.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I i was-- I suppose I was silly, because it was just bravery and nothing more.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I went into the German pharmacist which was just opposite where Lusia and Milek lived, and Milek saw me once going in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he had a weak heart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "As you know, he was ill before the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he saw me going in, and he couldn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he saw me coming out again with a parcel, and next time when he saw me, he asked, for heaven's sake, what did you do in the German pharmacy?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, well, I go there from time to time to get some cotton wool or bandages which Mrs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Stelmachowska needs for her nurseries.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was aghast.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, never, never do that again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they saw me, and I spoke good German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I said, I would like to have some cotton wool and some elastoplast, or what-- little things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Once they asked me whether I have a identity card.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Naturally, they thought a German would have identity card.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have a identity card.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I didn't have one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So if they would have found that out, that I am Polish-- well, I'm not talking about Jewish, but Polish-- I wouldn't have come out of this.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I had to promise Milek that I never will do that again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I can't tell much more about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
